        {
            "title": "2025年大漲27%後：七大頂級AI策略再斬獲25.5%收益",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iOuYEr7Mm0aKihysYHqroA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/moved_LYNXMPEL3M0QK_L.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com – 市场刚刚度过了一个动荡不安的周末：中东的停火协议岌岌可危，特朗普威胁发动新一轮袭击，美军则在伊朗港口周围布下包围圈。市场立即作出反应：油价飙升，通胀担忧扼杀了市场对美联储加息的所有幻想。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在Docusign等软件股遭重挫、道琼斯指数迷失方向的背景下，我们的人工智能展现出了其抗危机能力。2026年的数据表明：<strong>7大最佳ProPicks策略</strong>已开启加速模式，目前<strong>平均收益率高达25.55%。</strong> 若对这种精准度存疑，只需回顾过去一年。<strong>2025年，全部88种AI策略均</strong> <strong>以27.19%的</strong>卓越<strong>平均回报率</strong>收官。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>2026年顶级策略精选：</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>韩国市场领军股：</strong>35.64%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美国能源精英：</strong>28.61%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>跑赢通胀：</strong>25.45%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>巴西稳健企业：</strong>21.00%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>跑赢WIG20指数 - 前10名：</strong>19.97%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>德国工业冠军股：</strong>15.28%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>西班牙价值机遇：</strong>13.98%</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至4月1日，各策略已重新进行权重调整。人工智能基于当前数据情况，决定了哪些仓位予以保留，以及通过获利了结为具有超额回报潜力的新股票腾出空间。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7ccd3afa-6c6c-36ce-8bf0-714d12e99db5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">总体而言，4 月份共有 12 种策略的命中率达到至少 90%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">这绝非个例，2026年所有88项ProPicks人工智能策略的总体概览便证明了这一点。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"771\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/f_CfbsSYgqKjCbQ1rBhnDA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc3MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/investing_com_hk_986/b3c2e1110c8fbcbbad3ebde4bcea9097\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong> 937只股票</strong>平均收益达<strong>+4.50%</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>命中率</strong>达<strong>67.26%</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">获利股票不仅占多数，其表现还比亏损股票高出+28.<strong> 78%</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">这意味着平均收益比平均亏损高出+28.78%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>67种策略</strong>实现了盈利</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>86只股票</strong>收益超过10%——平均收益为14.1%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最佳策略在4月份上涨了<strong> 9.5%</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最大超额收益为<strong>5.5%</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除两个例外（2025年2月和2026年3月）外，2025/26年度每个月的策略单项盈利总额均高于亏损总额。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XtN7x4gB.uwrHSmsl3cnUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTM5NA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/investing_com_hk_986/a604a9ff55b4841d27db549dc0be4b27\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><pre class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">（截至2026年4月13日）</pre><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2025年，前三名策略的回报率略高于69%，2026年甚至可能突破70%大关。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>AI是如何实现如此优异表现的？</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ProPicks AI旨在及早识别投资机会：即基本面强劲但尚未被市场充分关注的股票。我们的模型不会受新闻头条或炒作影响，而是对财务指标进行细致入微的分析——保持中立、客观且实时更新。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">这对你意味着：<strong>在这些股票价格高涨之前</strong>，你就能发现潜在的优胜者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">数据给出了明确的答案：ProPicks的选股策略完全达到了预期目标——它跑赢了大盘，而这正是投资中真正重要的唯一标准。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">关于 ProPicks 的具体运作原理以及如何充分利用它们，请观看此视频：</p><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, 56%)\"></div></blockquote><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">如果您已经是 Pro 会员<strong>，那么 4 月的最新精选已上线</strong>——您可以在 InvestingPro 仪表盘中直接查看。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"App用户可在此处查看。\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:App用户可在此处查看。;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://de.investing.com/apps/?screen=search_explorer&amp;section=strategy\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">App用户可在此处查看。</a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"网页用户可在此处查看。\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:网页用户可在此处查看。;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://de.investing.com/pro/propicks?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">网页用户可在此处查看。</a></p></li></ul></div>",
